editcount-all-namespaces: Table cell text in namespace column representing all namespaces.
editcount-count: Column header in result table for the number of edits.
editcount-namespace: Column header in result table for the namespaces.
editcount-percentage: Column header in result table for the percentages.
editcount-resulttitle: <h2> element for the title of the query result.
editcount-user: Username field label in special page form.
editcount-userdoesnotexist: An error message shown when a user account is not registered.
